4.2 Accepted Loans Dataset¶

This is a supplement to the main EDA notebook (1.1 EDA) that includes the individual analysis of all numerical and categorical variables. The insights obtained here together with the analysis of interaction between individual variables was used to build the preprocessing pipeline and individual transformers (for feature engineering) that were used when building our models (see the EDA notebook for additional details).
